<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَسَبِّحْهُ}</span> ... نَزِّهْهُ، وَعَظِّمْهُ، وَصَلِّ لَهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَإِدْبَارَ النُّجُومِ}</span> ... نَزِّهْهُ، وَصَلِّ لَهُ صَلَاةَ الصُّبْحِ وَقْتَ غَيْبَةِ النُّجُومِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>